      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example features a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a variable M differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive service of the double VANOS system to ensure optimal valve timing. The suspension geometry remains true, benefiting from refreshed bushings and dampers that maintain the chassis's signature neutral handling. This is a visceral, driver-oriented machine with linear power delivery and precise steering feedback, ideal for the enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical integrity and performance dynamics.",
